    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Laurens Winkelhagen</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:202px;\"><a href=\"http://www.arves.org/arves/index.php/en/halloffame/310-van-reek-jan-1945-2015\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/2/2f/LaurensWinkelhagen.jpg\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:LaurensWinkelhagen.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Laurens Winkelhagen <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Laurens Winkelhagen</b>,<br />\na Dutch computer scientist and senior software engineer. He holds a M.Sc. in <a href=\"/Artificial_Intelligence\" title=\"Artificial Intelligence\">artificial intelligence</a> from  <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Utrecht_University\">Utrecht University</a> in 2006. \nAs computer chess programmer, Laurens Winkelhagen is author of the chess engines <a href=\"/JanWillem\" title=\"JanWillem\">JanWillem</a>, released in 2004, and <a href=\"/FrankWalter\" title=\"FrankWalter\">FrankWalter</a>, first released in 2009 <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, revised in 2018 <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>, and published as <a href=\"/Category:Open_Source\" title=\"Category:Open Source\">open source</a> in February 2019 <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2004_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2004 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2018_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2018 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Laurens_Winkelhagen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laurens Winkelhagen</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://scholar.google.co.uk/citations?user=rvG4n98AAAAJ&amp;hl=en\">Mehdi Dastani</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=6AUsknwAAAAJ&amp;hl=en\">Jan Broersen</a> (<b>2005</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/11691792_1\">Beliefs in Agent Implementation</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/dalt/dalt2005.html\">DALT 2005</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Laurens_Winkelhagen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2004_...\">2004 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Laurens_Winkelhagen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2004 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=423\">JanWillem 1.09</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laurens Winkelhagen</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, October 29,  2004</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=752\">JanWillem</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laurens Winkelhagen</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, November 26, 2004</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=49948\">Java &amp; Magic Bitboards</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laurens Winkelhagen</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, February 03, 2009</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=50010\">Frank-Walter 1.0.5</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laurens Winkelhagen</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, March 03, 2009</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2018_...\">2018 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Laurens_Winkelhagen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2018 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?t=68989\">Revived Engine - Frank Walter 2.2.0 (Java - WB)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laurens Winkelhagen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 20, 2018</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=69754&amp;start=9\">Re: New engine releases 2019</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laurens Winkelhagen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 12, 2019</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Laurens_Winkelhagen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/ljgw\">ljgw (Laurens Winkelhagen) · GitHub</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/laurenswinkelhagen/\">Laurens Winkelhagen | LinkedIn</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Laurens_Winkelhagen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/laurenswinkelhagen/\">Laurens Winkelhagen | LinkedIn</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=50010\">Frank-Walter 1.0.5</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laurens Winkelhagen</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, March 03, 2009</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?t=68989\">Revived Engine - Frank Walter 2.2.0 (Java - WB)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laurens Winkelhagen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 20, 2018</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=69754&amp;start=9\">Re: New engine releases 2019</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Laurens Winkelhagen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 12, 2019</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/w/Winkelhagen:Laurens\">dblp: Laurens Winkelhagen</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301061635\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.018 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.020 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 97/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 206/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion dep